snippet.title: Tybot Invasion: The Typing Runner - Trailer
snippet.description:
Type words quickly to destroy robots, move among lanes, and destroy all the enemy's waves on this invasion that mixes Typing & Run! The future of Robworld is in your hands, can you destroy all robots fast enough? Type for your life. Type for the future.

Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1636000
